Sometimes troublesome monsters like Frosrin live in ruins. Frosrin is
a subspecies of goblin and is also called a burrow goblin.

These guys have a habit of expanding their underground burrows, and it
often connects to things like ancient underground ruins.

Each individual is not that strong, but they have a habit of acting in
groups. If you see one, there is sure to be a group of them at the
village level.

Of course, they don't just live in ruins, sometimes they make their
homes in underground burrows. They also have territories in the east,
so don't go there.
